The careless whispers

To the heart and mind
Ignorance is kind

[Instrumental]

As I take your hand
And lead you to the dance floor

Something in your eyes

Guilty feet have got no rhythm

The way I danced with you, oh

And waste a chance that I've been given
So I'm never gonna dance again
The way I danced with you, oh

Never without your love

[Bridge]

I wish that we could lose this crowd
Maybe it's better this way

That you had to leave me alone?

By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story shifts away from spectacle to explore the quiet aftermath of a hero who believed his battles were over. Set within Tobey Maguire’s Spider-Man universe, the narrative follows Peter Parker in retirement, having chosen family, stability, and a life defined by responsibility to those he loves rather than the mask he once wore. Years of sacrifice have earned him peace, but that peace is fragile, built on the hope that the world no longer needs him. When an unexpected threat reaches across realities, Peter is forced to confront the cost of walking away and the truth that some responsibilities never truly end. Torn between protecting the life he has built and answering a call only he can understand, the story frames his return not as destiny, but as choice. Avengers: Doomsday positions Spider-Man’s comeback as a deeply personal reckoning, where legacy, family, and duty collide, setting the stage for a conflict that threatens not just worlds, but the lives heroes fought to preserve.

snippet.title: BABYMETAL - ヘドバンギャー！！ 15th Night Ver. (OFFICIAL)
snippet.description:
BABYMETAL結成 15 周年を記念し「ヘドバンギャー！！ 」を再録！
本楽曲を収録した結成 15 周年を記念した超限定 CD を2026 年 1月 7 日(水)より東京・渋谷の SHIBUYA TSUTAYA 1 階にて開催される POP-UP ストア「BABYMETAL FIRST EVER POP-UP IN TOKYO」、および 2026 年 1 月 10 日(土)・11 日(日)にさいたまスーパーアリーナで開催されるスペシャル公演「LEGEND - METAL FORTH」のグッズ売場にて、数量限定で販売いたします。

購入特典として、CD をご購入いただいた方へ最新ミュージックビデオに登場する衣装のポストカード(全 3 種/ランダム封入)を 1 枚プレゼント。そのカードの中に結成15 周年を祝福するスペシャルな「THE CHOSEN 15 カード」が 15 枚限定で封入されています。
幸運な「選ばれし 15 人」は誰の手に!?
▶詳細：https://babymetal.com/headbangeeeeerrrrr15th

さらに、「ヘドバンギャー！！ 15th Night Ver.」のリリースを記念して、ミュージックビデオ内
でメンバーが着用した衣裳と同デザインのスタッズ付き「15th Night Studded Battle Long
Jacket」が 15 着限定で、本日よりオンラインストア「A!SMART」にて抽選販売が決定!
「15thNight Studded Battle Long Jacket」は POP-UP ストアで展示を予定しています。
▶詳細：http://www.asmart.jp/babymetal

Lyrics：EDOMETAL, NAKAMETAL

snippet.title: Launch Trailer I BLEACH: Thousand Year Blood War Part 3 I VIZ
snippet.description:
Experience every clash, every reveal, every moment, now yours to own. 💿
BLEACH: Thousand-Year Blood War Part 3 home video is here.

Get BLEACH: Thousand Year Blood War Part 3 on Blu-ray: https://bit.ly/3LjPhRG

About BLEACH: Thousand Year Blood War Part 3:

The blood war between Soul Reapers and Quincies intensifies after the Wandenreich’s second wave of attack transforms the Seireitei into a dimension known as the Schatten Bereich. Undaunted, the Thirteen Court Guard Squads reclaim their stolen Bankai to strike back and defeat several of the Stern Ritter’s most powerful members, the Wörtlich. As the battle wages on, Renji Abarai, Rukia Kuchiki, and finally Ichigo Kurosaki each complete their training at the Royal Palace and return to the Seireitei to help the Soul Reapers with their newly acquired powers and abilities. However, Ichigo’s attempt to stop Yhwach is thwarted by Uryu Ishida. A shocked Ichigo demands Uryu to explain his true intention for pointing his weapon toward his friends. But the only answer he gets from Uryu is a rain of arrows to signal the end of their friendship. With Uryu and the Royal Guards at his side, Yhwach successfully breaks past the Soul Shield Membrane barrier and finally sets foot into the sacred realm of the Royal Palace. But the Quincies’ advance seemingly ends after facing Squad Zero, who use their awesome powers to defeat Yhwach and the rest of the uninvited guests. However, the real battle and despair have yet to start… Soul Reapers and Quincies. Ichigo and Uryu. Beliefs and Resolve. The never-ending conflict between light and dark clashes above the dark-blue heavens.

2-Disc Blu-ray Set, 14 Episodes, 16x9 HD 1080p, English and Japanese Stereo Audio, English Subtitles

SPECIAL FEATURES: BLEACH: Thousand-Year Blood War - The Conflict NYCC 2024 Panel featuring Masakazu Morita and Noriaki Sugiyama, BLEACH: Thousand-Year Blood War Lookback (Episodes 25-38), SennaRin “Reaper” Official Music Video, Finale Special Opening and Ending Songs, Promotional Videos, Trailers

snippet.title: AVENGERS: DOOMSDAY (2026) | Black Panther Trailer | Marvel Comics | Concept
snippet.description:
#Marvel #Avengers #Avengersdoomsday #ChrisEvans #Robertdowneyjr 
 
🎥 Attention viewers! (ITS FAN MADE)
The Avengers: Doomsday Trailer teases an epic new chapter in the Marvel Cinematic Universe as Wakanda rises to face a world-ending threat in Avengers: Doomsday (2026). The Avengers Doomsday official trailer hints at the return of Robert Downey Jr. as Doctor Doom, setting up a powerful clash that reshapes the MCU and launches Marvel Phase 6. Packed with breathtaking action, comic-inspired visuals, and high-stakes drama, the Avengers Doomsday teaser trailer promises one of the most ambitious Marvel movies ever from Marvel Studios.

The inspiration behind this video:
The Avengers Doomsday trailer has finally dropped, and the road to Avengers 2026 officially begins now! In this video, we break down every explosive moment of the Avengers Doomsday official trailer, analyzing the destruction and the stakes for Earth's Mightiest Heroes. As Marvel Studios prepares for the biggest theatrical event of the year, we discuss how this Avengers Doomsday movie serves as the terrifying kickoff to Marvel Phase 6. Whether you are watching for the action or the lore, this breakdown of the Avengers Doomsday marvel trailer covers everything you need to know about the most anticipated Avengers Doomsday update yet.

The internet is still buzzing about the terrifying presence of Robert Downey Jr Doctor Doom. We dive deep into the massive Avengers Doomsday cast, debating whether this variant is a twisted version of Tony Stark or the true Victor Von Doom from the comics. This isn't just a team-up; the footage makes it look like a solo Doctor Doom movie where the villain finally wins. We analyze the Doctor Doom MCU suit upgrades and what the Avengers Doomsday teaser reveals about his war against the remaining Avengers. If you are here for the Robert Downey Jr MCU comeback, this video explores every theory regarding the Avengers Doctor Doom conflict.

Finally, we connect the dots between the lingering plot threads of MCU Phase 5 and the multiverse saga's climax in the Marvel Cinematic Universe. We hunt for easter eggs in the Dr Doom trailer footage and discuss how the doomsday trailer sets up the ultimate sacrifice. From the visual tone to the hidden cameos, we leave no stone unturned in this analysis. Don't miss our full reaction to the Avengers Doomsday trailer official release and our predictions for who survives the wrath of Marvel's greatest villain.
